args:
The party reaches Zethia, but she has already
become a host to the Other. When she departs,
King Aurelius's soul merges with Zodiark to give
chase on wing, leaving the prince to follow.
You'll not have your way... Not while I\nstill hold the Shadowwyrm's pact!
I won't allow you to lay a finger on her\never again, Other!
This time, I WILL keep her safe!
You fool! You have no idea what you're\ndoing!
Come away from her NOW! Before—
Before she stabs you in the back?
Wait, WHAT?! {player_name}!\nZethia, why did you just DO THAT?!
Hmmm, why indeed? It's such a mystery!
...Unless the rite is already complete and\nthe Auspex is no longer herself! Ah ha ha!
Well, isn't this sweet? You're still calling\nme by that name.
You needn't force it. I'm perfectly happy to\nbe called the Other.
The worst has come to pass...
Oh, what a marvelous body this is!\nMana courses and crackles within every\nlimb and digit! Every speck of flesh!
I feel as if I could unmake you all with the\nflick of a wrist. Shall we put it to the test?
Let's begin with family, shall we?\nReturn to dust, O dearest brother of mine!\nHAAAAAAH!
Now, let's see what remains of... What?!
I am a shameful excuse for a king...\nI allow my body to be taken, then fail to\nspare my daughter from...the same fate...
But you will not have...my son...
...Heh. Eeee hee hee! AAAAH HA HA HA!\nOh, but you ARE an amusing old fool!\nDo you really think you can change this?
You've traded your life to halt a single\nblow. Bought the boy a mere moment.
Stay strong, Father! Cleo, he needs—
No, {player_name}.\nMy body falters...but my will lives on!
Death is not the end for those who draw\nthe blood of dragons.
I leave the rest...to you, Shadowwyrm...\nAccept my soul as mana.
Our pact is ended. I place my trust in you.\nFollow your own...judgment...
Aurelius. Faithful master. Gentle king.\nYou would grant my freedom?
Then I shall see you avenged. Not as a\nvassal's duty, but as a friend's mourning.
Thus do I honor your sacrifice.
Wait. Father is becoming one with the\nShadowwyrm?
How deep their bond must be!
Tsk! The beast feeds on death itself and\ngrows stronger for it. That king is truly\na nuisance to the last...
But I've a more important task now than\ntoying with you all.
With the Auspex's body, I can now proceed\nto the chamber depths and draw the Flow\nEternal. Farewell!
Zethia! No, this can't be happening!
What is he planning to do with her body?
And saving my daughter is the same.\nLeave this to me.
It's Father! I can feel him!
My power earned me a seat among the\nSix Greatwyrms. Let it now banish this\nthreat from our world.
You must not follow. Leave this place and\nseek safety!
...He's gone. What do we do now,\n{player_name}?
I won't abandon Zethia or Zodiark,\nand I won't leave the Other unchecked.
He mentioned something called the Flow\nEternal, right? What new horror could he\npossibly be plotting?
